      "content": "i know there are resources, but they don't do anything for the actual reality of it. they just suggest more meds or therapy that doesn't work. it feels like everyone is just trying to \"fix\" something that is fundamentally broken. like, what am i supposed to do when the only thing that feels like it would actually bring relief is just... permanent stillness? it doesn't feel like a \"crisis,\" it just feels like a logical conclusion to the pain.",
